block content
  link(rel="stylesheet", href="/index.css")
  h1 Best Website Ever!
  p This website is dedicated to report on population information. It is a cutting-edge platform that has been designed to provide easy access to a vast array of data related to populations. The website is built on a SQL database system that ensures fast and efficient data retrieval, making it easy for users to find the information you need quickly.
  p The website features a modern, user-friendly interface that is easy to navigate, allowing users to filter and sort through the data with ease. Users can search for information on specific countries, cities, and population.
  p Whether you're a researcher, government agency, or just someone with an interest in population information, this website is the go-to resource for reliable and comprehensive data. With its user-friendly interface, customizable reports, and powerful data tools, the website is sure to become an essential tool for anyone looking to explore population information.

  p /countries type 'the world', a continent, or region.
  form(action='/countries', method='POST')
    input(type="text" name="place" placeholder="Enter 'the world', a continent, or region.")
    input(type="text" name="N" placeholder="Enter how many to display, type all for all.")
    input(type='submit' value='Submit')

  p /cities type 'the world', a continent, region, country, or district.
  form(action='/cities', method='POST')
